  m_Name: TutorialDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  npcName: Old Man
  npcPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d952a851392a84c4a8a1ed51430131fd, type: 3}
  dialogueLines1:
  - Come here young man....
  - Long have I watched this land, and long have I waited for someone who can gamble
    like you
  - Long have I watched this land, and long have I waited for someone who can gamble
    like you
  - This world is not as simple as it seems. Where money talks, only those smart
    enough to gamble their way to the top can survive
  - But words alone mean little
  - Show me....do you have the strength to walk this path?
  dialogueLines2:
  - You've proven yourself strong enough to take on the casinos.
  - You need to bring balance to gambling by defeating the 4 casinos!
  - Seek the casinos of ice, sand, grass, and evil.
  - Forge your own path, some may be harder than others but that is for you to discover.
  - You're the final hope, now BEGONE!
  dialogueLines3:
  - Welcome back promised one.
  - It appears you've suffered a fatal blow.
  - Fear not, this was expected.
  - To help you in your journey I will grant you a portion of my strength, in exchange
    of proofs of your triumphs.
  - Seek strength young one.
  dialogueLines4:
  - Prepare yourself to face the casinos again, this time a little stronger than
    before.
  - Best of luck young one.
  CombatEnemy: 1
  combatTransitionDelay: 2
  combatSceneName: CombatTutorial
